rows.label: qev041304_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ciniculas are a royal pain when you're in the field
on a search mission, but seeing them in card form is
kind of awesome.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041304_MSG0002
rows.name:
It would be great to stare at a cinicula Miralife Card
after bagging a big one in the field, but I just can't
seem to draw one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041304_MSG0003
rows.name:
You know your luck's bad when you can't even get the
bronze card you're after. Sheesh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041304_MSG0004
rows.name: ...What, you're looking to trade Miralife Cards?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041304_MSG0005
rows.name:
Well, I am DEFINITELY interested in that bronze
cinicula, but I don't really have any good cards to
trade for it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041304_MSG0006
rows.name:
Although I DO have this coupon for one free meal
at the diner! Their roast beef is just to die for.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041304_MSG0007
rows.name:
Sweet! And hey, if you find someone hungry enough
you could probably trade that for a Miralife Card.
...Hell, I did![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041304_MSG0009
rows.name: Aw, come on. Have you HAD the roast beef?[ST:wait ]
